np.testing.assert_array_equal(self.Inserts.top.set('B3', 'inserts'), self.
    Inserts.top)
np.testing.assert_array_equal(self.Inserts.bot.set('B3', 'inserts_bot'),
    self.Inserts.bot)
self.Inserts['top', 'A2'] = 'Bob'
self.assertEqual(self.Inserts[0, 'A2'], 'Bob')
self.Inserts['bot', 'A2'] = 'Bibi'
self.assertEqual(self.Inserts[1, 'A2'], 'Bibi')
